{"tid":91537,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Nikon 轉會定Upgrade 好？","createTime":"2017-01-23T02:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T00:44:03.000Z","uid":13437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebfea67b4798b0c4b2a76dc3818d0d14322a4210","tid":91537,"uid":13437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"本身用緊D5200 +s1835.8 +18105 kit lens<br />\n<br />\n影出黎既相唔多滿意，例如話，對準焦都好，成張相既感覺唔夠銳利，而且夜晚影相，ISO set 做Auto (up to 3200), 張相d 粒粒好明顯，張相好唔討好。<br />\n<br />\nSetting: 影RAW (Fine),光圈先決<br />\n<br />\n我睇過幾部機，唔知邊部比較好<br />\n<br />\n1. D500 <br />\n雖然枝s1835.8可以用得番，唔需要放，但我想知D500 影夜間Snap Shot 會唔會都係唔討好？<br />\n<br />\n2. D750<br />\n舊過D500﹐連拍慢少少，但FF 機影夜景應該會討好d?<br />\n<br />\n3. Canon 5D Mark 3 <br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e5d04b6e116a8fc7e5657dc5a4d865dc9e3ba8","tid":91537,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:46:01.000Z","msg":"你用auto iso俾你用到D5都係死<br />\n<br />\n正常夜景相要腳架+iso 100+收光圈到f/8-F/11,MF對焦,kit鏡都sharp"},{"pid":"65c01e5038cc3a687f66a856af2e7b512c0cb199","tid":91537,"uid":13437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你用auto iso俾你用到D5都係死<br />\n<br />\n正常夜景相要腳架+iso 100+收光圈到f/8-F/11,MF對焦,kit鏡都sharp</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理解影夜影要落腳架，但平日係街影一張半張（有街燈）既情況下，冇理由下下都腳架咁唔方便。<br />\n<br />\n用埋我想知Auto ISO(up to 3200) 有咩問題？我知ISO 太高會令張相起粒粒，但3200 都算好高？"},{"pid":"d6b371667b12ffc4e840a7d8d01b4ffcfb08b4da","tid":91537,"uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你用auto iso俾你用到D5都係死<br />\n<br />\n正常夜景相要腳架+iso 100+收光圈到f/8-F/11,MF對焦,kit鏡都sharp</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理解影夜影要落腳架，但平日係街影一張半張（有街燈